<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><presentation>v1 v2 </presentation>
<aka>Takk min Gud</aka>
<key>E</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Thank you Lord
 for saving my soul.
 Thank you Lord
 for making me whole.
 Thank you Lord
 for giving to me,
 Thy great salvation
 so full and free.

[V2]
 Takk min Gud,
 Du frelste min sjel.
 Takk min Gud,
 Du gjorde meg hel.
 Takk min Gud,
 at du ville gi
 Din store Frelse
 så rik og fri</lyrics>
<title>Thank you Lord for saving my soul</title>
</song>